text: The III CELAC summit or 2015 CELAC summit was the third ordinary heads of state summit of the Community of Latin American and Caribbean States. It was held on 28 and 29 January 2015 in San José, Costa Rica. == References == == External links == * Official declaration (Spanish) Category:2015 conferences Category:2015 in international relations Category:2015 in South America Category:2015 in the Caribbean Category:Diplomatic conferences in Costa Rica Summit,2015 Category:January 2015 events in South America
